id="tab-id-2-container" class="tab_content "><div
class="tab_inner_content invers-color"  itemprop="text" ><h4>Improve Product Portfolio Value and Time to Market</h4><p>Our solution supports the end-to-end new product development cycle, helping you manage idea-to-launch processes, prioritize R&#038;D investments, optimize the allocation of resources, and strike the right portfolio balance between new and existing products.</p><div
